sentence: Consumer shares were mainly unchanged ahead of the opening bell on Wednesday.
In consumer stocks news, SuperValu ( SVU ) announced Wednesday that it has appointed Mark Gross president and chief executive officer of the grocery wholesaler.
He replaces Sam Duncan who retires effective February 29, 2016.
Shares in the company were flat at $4.34 pre-bell.
The company has traded between $3.99 and $12 over the past 52 weeks.
Home Depot ( HD ) said it is hiring more than 80,000 associated nationwide for its nearly 2,000 stores as it prepares for the busiest selling season.
Shares in the company were flat at $125.27 pre-bell.
The company has traded between $92.17 and $135.47 over the past 52 weeks.
